{"tid":1513814,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［每晚十點］藍絲家庭演唱會指南","createTime":"2019-08-28T13:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T12:12:27.000Z","uid":107092,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac22e26749de9b2dd62e6e215b128d1e8e73384f","tid":1513814,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:20:07.000Z","msg":"小弟生於藍絲家庭，<br />\n堅持每晚十點左右就會出去掉垃圾，<br />\n家母最近讚我好乖每日準時掉垃圾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每晚十點左右話自己：<br />\n出去倒垃圾、<br />\n落街做運動、<br />\n落去買嘢飲、<br />\n出街陪朋友...<br />\n<br />\n然後出去：<br />\n後樓梯、<br />\n樓下公園、<br />\n隱蔽地方...<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n後樓梯必須去隔離巷+上/落幾層，<br />\n再關埋防煙門。<br />\n小弟試過偷懶就咁去近嘅後樓梯，<br />\n屋企人戴住耳機打機都聽到。<br />\n<br />\n注意安全、保持戒心，<br />\n唔好以為冇危險，<br />\n試過嗌完之後聽到屌你老母+開門聲，<br />\n嚇到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n另外冇回應嘅唔好灰心，<br />\n我見證住由冇人嗌，<br />\n一把聲、兩把聲，變到開始嘈，<br />\n唔好睇小自己嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9a7faa43b5dea7ce3dcbdf59c51dfaa88ef6dd","tid":1513814,"uid":107092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"將軍澳巴打準備就緒！"},{"pid":"2016701a2df7d528b565bc82fb465dfecfe44721","tid":1513814,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:22:32.000Z","msg":"831！<br />\n901！"},{"pid":"6043df13f4f968c9b2c43103c2078d825a4cf524","tid":1513814,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊"},{"pid":"6b5b075da066e48b245982900d505fe9fbd4bd94","tid":1513814,"uid":107092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"時代革命啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！"},{"pid":"884b6bd4f58bf2e0398dd76b79b51b6bceb4afda","tid":1513814,"